      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the high-revving S54 inline-six engine, boasting a pristine 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous transitional throttle response. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled, the rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance, and the rear subframe reinforced to exceed factory structural specifications. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, riding on factory-spec dampers with all bushings exhibiting zero deflection. Finished in collector-grade condition with matching VIN tags on all panels, this vehicle represents a turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking OEM+ mechanical excellence.",
